title: wp.tgz
description:
Alright guys. Most of this is a repack for convenience. There are 206 themes and 82 plugins in this pack. All themes (to the best of my knowledge) are from 2013. All plugins are from CodeCanyon.

No multi-compressed stuff - single .tgz file to extract, and you will have a directory full of themes and one full of plugins.

To Use:

Themes: Either use the WordPress theme uploader, or upload them with FTP/SFTP to /wp-content/themes/

They will automatically show up in WordPress when you go to yoursite.com/wp-admin -> Appearance/Themes

Plugins: Same idea as above - upload them via WordPress, FTP or SFTP to /wp-content/plugins. Go to yoursite.com/wp-admin/ -> Plugins and activate to your hearts desire.

Enjoy and seed!
